# Tippmix.hu Integration Plan

## Goal Description
Integrate live match data and odds from `tippmix.hu` into the existing Table Tennis Analyzer app. This will allow users to see real-time odds alongside the statistical analysis.

## User Review Required
> [!IMPORTANT]
> **CORS / Data Access**: Fetching data directly from `tippmix.hu` via a browser-based app (client-side) is likely blocked by CORS policies. We may need to use a CORS proxy (like `cors-anywhere`) or a simple local backend server. I will investigate the best approach.

